name: Hungry Aliens
description:
In this game you will be playing as a alien operating a UFO. The alien  however is very hungry so you have to help the alien get food while dodging the lightning and waves coming for your alien.  To get food to the alien the UFO will suck the fish out of the water and into his ship where he can eat it, you do not want to eat the puffer fish because it is poisonous. When you die you will get your score and if you want you can play again.

*Also ignore the quit to desktop button, I am too lazy to get rid of it.
